  ('dietitian-moex-00493', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-113-2755cf97', 'sub-dietitian-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '有關灌食的方法，下列何者正確？', '["批次灌食法（bolus enteral feeding）適合用在空腸造口的病人", "間歇灌食法（intermittent enteral feeding）的起始灌食量建議為250～300 c.c.", "連續灌食法（continuous enteral feeding）可以目標流速的1/4流速開始灌食", "提供高滲透壓配方時，最好稀釋配方來增加腸道耐受度"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:50+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "21691dff4ad8", "answer_pdf_sha1": "006b7e686bce", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "113030", "c": "102", "s": "11", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "膳食療養學", "year": "113", "exam_name": "113年第一次專技人員高等考試營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試", "original_question_number": 4, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('dietitian-moex-00494', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-113-2755cf97', 'sub-dietitian-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '對於使用呼吸器的重症病人，下列有關早期等熱量（early isocaloric）靜脈營養和腸道營養的敘述，何者最 適當？', '["腸道營養比靜脈營養有較低的死亡率", "腸道營養比靜脈營養有較高的二次感染（second infection）風險", "腸道營養比靜脈營養有較低的消化道併發症風險", "腸道營養比靜脈營養有較低的加護病房住院時間"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:50+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "21691dff4ad8", "answer_pdf_sha1": "006b7e686bce", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "113030", "c": "102", "s": "11", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "膳食療養學", "year": "113", "exam_name": "113年第一次專技人員高等考試營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試", "original_question_number": 5, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
